messages.message:
Cypress tests have been failing to run on master and release branches via Jenkins. I tried fixing it, but that doesn't work. I'm going to try to port them over to GitHub Actions:
Latest run (in progress): https://cloud.cypress.io/projects/cfhedy/runs/22164/overview?roarHideRunsWithDiffGroupsAndTags=1
PR: https://github.com/instabase/instabase/actions/runs/17600671878/job/50001929115?pr=74473

Ironically, just after I post this, Cypress on aihub-sandbox via Jenkins was able to start. Last success run was 21 days ago tho :sweat:
